Slider_SetBounds
#include Style
#Background wimp 1
Module:	<Window=>window/m>
#Line
#Wrap off
Veneer:	<slider_set_bounds>
Syntax:	Slider_SetBounds
#indent

On Entry:
#indent 6
{FCode}r0 = flags
     bit 0 - set lower bound
     bit 1 - set upper bound
     bit 2 - set step size
r1 = window object Id
r2 = 578
r3 = gadget component Id
r4 = lower bound
r5 = upper bound
r6 = step size
{f}
#indent
On exit:
#indent 6
{FCode}r1-r9 preserved
{f}
#indent
#Wrap
Purpose:	Method sets the bounding values of the slider.